""आप केवल कंपनी द्वारा प्रदान किए गए अपने खाते का उपयोग करने के अधिकार का आनंद लेंगे; आप अपने इंटरनेट प्लेटफ़ॉर्म खाते के लिए ज़िम्मेदार होंगे और केवल आप ही अपने खाते का उपयोग कर सकते हैं; यदि आप अपने खाते का उपयोग करने के अधिकार को हस्तांतरित, श्रेष्ठ या अधिकृत करते हैं। अन्य लोगों को, कंपनी को लिखित रूप में अधिसूचित किया जाएगा और उत्तराधिकारी को उक्त खाते का उपयोग करने का कानूनी अधिकार प्राप्त होगा जब तक कि कंपनी इस बात से सहमत न हो और उक्त उत्तराधिकारी इस समझौते पर हस्ताक्षर करता है, अन्यथा, कंपनी को सभी को निलंबित करने या समाप्त करने का अधिकार होगा; किसी भी समय किसी भी जिम्मेदारियों को प्रभावित किए बिना आपको प्रदान की गई सेवाएं।
6. चूँकि कंपनी आपके उपयोगकर्ता नाम और पासवर्ड के माध्यम से आपके निर्देश को पहचान लेगी, इसलिए आप अपने उपयोगकर्ता नाम और पासवर्ड का अच्छे से ध्यान रखेंगे और पासवर्ड के संपर्क में आने के कारण होने वाली किसी भी हानि या परिणाम को आपके द्वारा ही पूरा किया जाएगा। आप अपने खाते और पासवर्ड को किसी के सामने प्रकट नहीं करने और किसी और के इंटरनेट प्लेटफ़ॉर्म खाते और पासवर्ड का उपयोग न करने के लिए वारंट देंगे।
7. यदि आपको कोई ऐसी स्थिति मिलती है, जहां अन्य लोगों ने आपके खाते और पासवर्ड या किसी अन्य अवैध प्राधिकरण को चोरी या अवैध रूप से उपयोग किया है, तो आप कंपनी को तुरंत और प्रभावी रूप से सूचित करेंगे और कंपनी से प्रासंगिक सेवाओं को निलंबित करने का अनुरोध करेंगे। उसी समय, आप समझेंगे कि आपके अनुरोध के अनुसार किसी भी कार्रवाई से पहले एक उचित अवधि होगी, और इसलिए कंपनी उस अवधि से पहले किसी भी लागू निर्देशों के कारण किसी भी नुकसान के लिए जिम्मेदार नहीं होगी।
8. यह समझौता इसके उपबंधों और वेबसाइट पर प्रकाशित सभी नियमों से बना होगा। संबंधित संज्ञा को उद्धृत किया जा सकता है और पारस्परिक रूप से संदर्भित किया जा सकता है। यदि कोई अलग समझ है, तो इसके कारण खंड प्रबल होंगे।
""","5. คุณมีสิทธิ์ใช้บัญชีที่ทางบริษัทฯให้มาเท่านั้น คุณมีหน้าที่ดูแลบัญชีแพลตฟอร์มอินเทอร์เน็ตของคุณ และมีแต่คุณคนเดียวเท่านั้นที่สามารถใช้บัญชีของคุณได้ หากคุณต้องการโอน ส่งหรือมอบหมายสิทธิ์การใช้บัญชีของคุณให้กับบุคคลอื่น ควรแจ้งให้ทางบริษัทฯทราบเป็นลายลักษณ์อักษร และหลังจากทางบริษัทฯตกลงและลงนามในข้อตกลงนี้แล้ว ผู้สืบทอดถึงจะได้รับสิทธิ์ในการใช้บัญชีอย่างถูกต้อง มิฉะนั้น บริษัทมีสิทธิ์ที่จะระงับหรือยุติบริการทั้งหมดที่มีให้คุณได้ตลอดเวลา โดยไม่ต้องรับผิดชอบใดๆ ทั้งสิ้น

UIRemittance_explain,"1. After starting the order, in your banking app, transfer the money to clabe. Close the deal. \n2. After a successful remittance, the remittanceamount will be added to your platform balance\n3. The minimum amount for a single top-up is 50","1. ऑर्डर शुरू करने के बाद अपने बैंकिंग ऐप में पैसे को क्लैब में ट्रांसफर करें। सौदा कर लो।\n2. सफल प्रेषण के बाद, प्रेषण राशि आपके प्लेटफ़ॉर्म बैलेंस में जोड़ दी जाएगी\n3. एकल टॉप-अप के लिए न्यूनतम राशि 50 है",1. หลังจากเริ่มสั่งซื้อแล้ว ให้โอนเงินไปที่ clabe ในแอปธนาคารของคุณ ปิดข้อตกลง.\n2. หลังจากการโอนเงินสำเร็จ จำนวนเงินที่โอนจะถูกเพิ่มไปยังยอดคงเหลือแพลตฟอร์มของคุณ\n3. จำนวนเงินขั้นต่ำสำหรับการเติมเงินครั้งเดียวคือ 50,"1. After starting the order, in your banking app, transfer the money to clabe. Close the deal.\n2. After a successful remittance, the remittanceamount will be added to your platform balance\n3. The minimum amount for a single top-up is 50",1. 開始訂單後，在您的銀行應用程序中，將錢轉至clabe。關閉交易。\n2. 匯款成功後，匯款金額將添加到您的平台餘額中\n3. 單次充值最低金額為50,"1. Sau khi bắt đầu đặt hàng, trong ứng dụng ngân hàng của bạn, hãy chuyển tiền đến clabe. Chốt giao dịch.\n2. Sau khi chuyển tiền thành công, số tiền chuyển sẽ được thêm vào số dư nền tảng của bạn\n3. Số tiền tối thiểu cho một lần nạp tiền là 50","1. Setelah memulai pemesanan, di aplikasi perbankan Anda, transfer uang ke clabe. Tutup kesepakatannya.\n2. Setelah pengiriman uang berhasil, jumlah pengiriman uang akan ditambahkan ke saldo platform Anda\n3. Jumlah minimum untuk sekali isi ulang adalah 50","1. ఆర్డర్‌ని ప్రారంభించిన తర్వాత, మీ బ్యాంకింగ్ యాప్‌లో, డబ్బును క్లాబ్‌కి బదిలీ చేయండి. ఒప్పందాన్ని మూసివేయండి.\n2. విజయవంతమైన చెల్లింపు తర్వాత, చెల్లింపు మొత్తం మీ ప్లాట్‌ఫారమ్ బ్యాలెన్స్‌కి జోడించబడుతుంది\n3. ఒక్క టాప్-అప్ కోసం కనీస మొత్తం 50","1. ऑर्डर सुरू केल्यानंतर, तुमच्या बँकिंग अॅपमध्ये, पैसे क्लेबमध्ये हस्तांतरित करा. करार बंद करा.\n2. यशस्वी रेमिटन्सनंतर, रेमिटन्सची रक्कम तुमच्या प्लॅटफॉर्म शिल्लकमध्ये जोडली जाईल\n3. एका टॉप-अपसाठी किमान रक्कम 50 आहे","1. Após iniciar o pedido, no seu aplicativo do banco, transfira o dinheiro para o clabe. Feche o negócio.\n2. Após uma remessa bem-sucedida, o valor da remessa será adicionado ao saldo da sua plataforma\n3. O valor mínimo para uma única recarga é 50","1. Después de iniciar el pedido, en tu aplicación bancaria, transfiere el dinero a clabe. Cerrar el trato.\n2. Después de una remesa exitosa, el monto de la remesa se agregará al saldo de su plataforma.\n3. El importe mínimo para una única recarga es 50"

Game1380_36,"● At every spin, any combinations of 4 or more symbols touching horizontally or vertically will result in a winning combination.","● At every spin, any combinations of 4 or more symbols touching horizontally or vertically will result in a winning combination.",● ในการหมุนทุกครั้ง ชุดสัญลักษณ์ที่มีสัญลักษณ์ 4 ตัวหรือ มากกว่าสัมผัสกันในแนวตั้งหรือแนวนอนจะสร้างชุดสัญลักษณ์ที่ ชนะรางวัล,"● At every spin, any combinations of 4 or more symbols touching horizontally or vertically will result in a winning combination.","● 每次旋轉時，水平或垂直接觸的 4 個或更多符號的任何組合都將產生獲勝組合。","● At every spin, any combinations of 4 or more symbols touching horizontally or vertically will result in a winning combination.","● Pada setiap putaran, kombinasi apa pun yang terdiri dari 4 simbol atau lebih yang bersentuhan secara horizontal atau vertikal akan menghasilkan kombinasi kemenangan.","● At every spin, any combinations of 4 or more symbols touching horizontally or vertically will result in a winning combination.","● At every spin, any combinations of 4 or more symbols touching horizontally or vertically will result in a winning combination.","● Em cada rodada, quaisquer combinações de 4 ou mais símbolos adjacentes na horizontal ou na vertical formam uma combinação vencedora.","● En cada giro, cualquier combinación de 4 o más símbolos que se toquen en horizontal o vertical generarán una combinación ganadora."
Game1380_37,"● For every winning combination, payout is made for each symbol according to the Paytable.","● For every winning combination, payout is made for each symbol according to the Paytable.",● สำหรับทุกชุดสัญลักษณ์ที่ชนะรางวัล จะมีการจ่ายรางวัลสำหรับสัญลักษณ์แต่ละตัวตามตารางการจ่ายรางวัล,"● For every winning combination, payout is made for each symbol according to the Paytable.","● 對於每個獲勝組合，根據賠率表對每個符號進行支付。","● For every winning combination, payout is made for each symbol according to the Paytable.","● Untuk setiap kombinasi kemenangan, bayaran diberikan untuk setiap simbol sesuai dengan Tabel Bayaran.","● For every winning combination, payout is made for each symbol according to the Paytable.","● For every winning combination, payout is made for each symbol according to the Paytable.","● Por cada combinação vencedora,é efetuado um pagamento por cada símbolo de acordo com a Tabela de pagamentos.","● Por cada combinación ganadora, se realizará el pago para cada símbolo de acuerdo con la Tabla de premios."

UI_Game970_help1,"4 Scatter symbols appearing anywhere will trigger  the Free Spins Feature with 10 free spins,5 Scatters-20  Free Spins, 6 Scatters-30 Free Spins.
If 3 or more Scatters drop during the Bonus Round  player gets 5 additional free spins.","कहीं भी दिखाई देने वाले 4 स्कैटर सिंबल 10 फ्री स्पिन, 5 स्कैटर-20 फ्री स्पिन, 6 स्कैटर-30 फ्री स्पिन के साथ फ्री स्पिन फीचर को ट्रिगर करेंगे।",สัญลักษณ์ Scatter 4 อันที่ปรากฏขึ้นที่ใดก็ได้จะเปิดใช้งานฟีเจอร์ Free Spins พร้อม 10 ฟรีสปิน 5 Scatters-20 Free Spins 6 Scatters-30 Free Spins
หาก Scatters 3 อันขึ้นไปหล่นระหว่างรอบโบนัส ผู้เล่นจะได้รับ 5 ฟรีสปินเพิ่มเติม,"4 Scatter symbols appearing anywhere will trigger  the Free Spins Feature with 10 free spins,5 Scatters-20  Free Spins, 6 Scatters-30 Free Spins.
If 3 or more Scatters drop during the Bonus Round  player gets 5 additional free spins.",出現在任何地方的 4 個散點符號將觸發免費旋轉功能，包括 10 次免費旋轉、5 次散點 - 20 次免費旋轉、6 次散點 - 30 次免費旋轉。
如果在獎金回合期間掉落 3 個或更多散點，玩家將獲得 5 次額外的免費旋轉。,"4 biểu tượng Scatter xuất hiện ở bất cứ đâu sẽ kích hoạt  Tính năng Vòng quay miễn phí với 10 vòng quay miễn phí, 5 Scatters-20  Vòng quay miễn phí, 6 Scatters-30 Vòng quay miễn phí.
Nếu 3 Scatters trở lên rơi ra trong Vòng thưởng  người chơi sẽ nhận được thêm 5 vòng quay miễn phí.","4 simbol Scatter yang muncul di mana saja akan memicu  Fitur Free Spins dengan 10 free spin, 5 Scatters-20  Free Spins, 6 Scatters-30 Free Spins.
Jika 3 atau lebih Scatters jatuh selama Putaran Bonus, pemain mendapatkan 5 free spin tambahan.","4 Scatter symbols appearing anywhere will trigger  the Free Spins Feature with 10 free spins,5 Scatters-20  Free Spins, 6 Scatters-30 Free Spins.
If 3 or more Scatters drop during the Bonus Round  player gets 5 additional free spins.","4 Scatter symbols appearing anywhere will trigger  the Free Spins Feature with 10 free spins,5 Scatters-20  Free Spins, 6 Scatters-30 Free Spins.
If 3 or more Scatters drop during the Bonus Round  player gets 5 additional free spins.","4 símbolos Scatter aparecendo em qualquer lugar ativarão o recurso Free Spins com 10 free spins, 5 Scatters-20 Free Spins, 6 Scatters-30 Free Spins.
Se 3 ou mais Scatters caírem durante a Rodada de Bônus, o jogador ganha 5 rodadas grátis adicionais.","Si aparecen 4 símbolos Scatter en cualquier lugar, se activará la función de giros gratis con 10 giros gratis, 5 Scatter-20  Giros gratis, 6 Scatter-30 Giros gratis.
Si aparecen 3 o más Scatter durante la ronda de bonificación, el jugador obtiene 5 giros gratis adicionales."

UI_Game970_help2,"Multiplier symbol is present on  the reels only during the Free  Spins Round. Whenever the  symbol hits it takes a random  multiplier value from 2x to  100x.
When the tumbling sequence ends, the value of all multiplier symbols on the screen are  added together and the total win of the sequence is multiplied by the final value.",गुणक प्रतीक केवल फ्री स्पिन राउंड के दौरान रीलों पर मौजूद होता है। जब भी प्रतीक हिट होता है तो यह 2x से 100x तक एक यादृच्छिक गुणक मान लेता है।,สัญลักษณ์ตัวคูณจะปรากฏบนวงล้อระหว่างรอบการหมุนฟรีเท่านั้น เมื่อไรก็ตามที่สัญลักษณ์กระทบ มันจะใช้ค่าตัวคูณแบบสุ่มตั้งแต่ 2x ถึง 100x
เมื่อลำดับไม้ลอยสิ้นสุดลง ค่าของสัญลักษณ์ตัวคูณทั้งหมดบนหน้าจอจะถูกบวกเข้าด้วยกัน และการชนะทั้งหมดของลำดับจะคูณด้วยค่าสุดท้าย,"Multiplier symbol is present on  the reels only during the Free  Spins Round. Whenever the  symbol hits it takes a random  multiplier value from 2x to  100x.
When the tumbling sequence ends, the value of all multiplier symbols on the screen are  added together and the total win of the sequence is multiplied by the final value.",乘數符號僅在免費旋轉回合期間出現在捲軸上。 每當符號命中時，它都會採用一個從 2x 到 100x 的隨機乘數。
當翻滾序列結束時，屏幕上所有乘數符號的值將加在一起，序列的總贏額乘以最終值。,"Biểu tượng số nhân chỉ xuất hiện trên  guồng trong Vòng quay  Miễn phí. Bất cứ khi nào biểu tượng chạm trúng, nó sẽ nhận một giá trị số nhân ngẫu nhiên từ 2x đến 100x.
Khi chuỗi lộn xộn kết thúc, giá trị của tất cả các biểu tượng số nhân trên màn hình được cộng lại với nhau và tổng số tiền thắng của chuỗi được nhân với giá trị cuối cùng.","Simbol pengali hanya ada di gulungan selama Putaran Putaran Gratis. Setiap kali  simbol mengenai, dibutuhkan nilai pengali acak dari 2x hingga 100x.
Saat urutan jatuh berakhir, nilai semua simbol pengali di layar dijumlahkan bersama dan total kemenangan urutan dikalikan dengan nilai akhir.","Multiplier symbol is present on  the reels only during the Free  Spins Round. Whenever the  symbol hits it takes a random  multiplier value from 2x to  100x.
When the tumbling sequence ends, the value of all multiplier symbols on the screen are  added together and the total win of the sequence is multiplied by the final value.","Multiplier symbol is present on  the reels only during the Free  Spins Round. Whenever the  symbol hits it takes a random  multiplier value from 2x to  100x.
When the tumbling sequence ends, the value of all multiplier symbols on the screen are  added together and the total win of the sequence is multiplied by the final value.","O símbolo do multiplicador está presente nas bobinas apenas durante a Rodada de Rodadas Grátis. Sempre que o símbolo atinge, ele recebe um valor multiplicador aleatório de 2x a 100x.
Quando a sequência cambaleante termina, o valor de todos os símbolos multiplicadores na tela são somados e o ganho total da sequência é multiplicado pelo valor final.","El símbolo multiplicador está presente en los carretes solo durante la ronda de giros gratis. Cada vez que el símbolo aparece, toma un valor multiplicador aleatorio de 2x a 100x.
Cuando finaliza la secuencia de volteretas, el valor de todos los símbolos multiplicadores en la pantalla se suma y la ganancia total de la secuencia se multiplica por el valor final."

UI_Game970_help4,"A player can buy a bonus at the price pictured above the button. If the player  increases the bet, the buy bonus price will be automatically increased. The next spin triggers a bonus game.","एक खिलाड़ी बटन के ऊपर चित्रित कीमत पर बोनस खरीद सकता है। यदि खिलाड़ी दांव बढ़ाता है, तो खरीद बोनस की कीमत अपने आप बढ़ जाएगी। स्पिन बोनस खरीदने के बाद शुरू होते हैं। अगला स्पिन एक बोनस गेम को ट्रिगर करता है।",ผู้เล่นสามารถซื้อโบนัสได้ในราคาที่แสดงไว้เหนือปุ่ม หากผู้เล่นเพิ่มเงินเดิมพัน ราคาโบนัสการซื้อจะเพิ่มขึ้นโดยอัตโนมัติ สปินเริ่มต้นหลังจากซื้อโบนัส การหมุนครั้งต่อไปจะเรียกเกมโบนัส,"A player can buy a bonus at the price pictured above the button. Nếu người chơi tăng tiền đặt cược, giá tiền thưởng mua sẽ tự động tăng lên. Vòng quay bắt đầu sau khi mua tiền thưởng. Putaran berikutnya memicu permainan bonus.","A player can buy a bonus at the price pictured above the button. If the player  increases the bet, the buy bonus price will be automatically increased. Spins start after buying  the bonus. The next spin triggers a bonus game.","A player can buy a bonus at the price pictured above the button. If the player  increases the bet, the buy bonus price will be automatically increased. Spins start after buying  the bonus. The next spin triggers a bonus game.","Um jogador pode comprar um bônus pelo preço mostrado acima do botão. Se o jogador aumentar a aposta, o preço do bônus de compra será aumentado automaticamente. Os giros começam após a compra do bônus. A próxima rodada aciona um jogo de bônus.","Un jugador puede comprar un bono al precio que se muestra arriba del botón. At the beginning of each round, 1 card is placed face up on the table. (This card will define the "Flip" that will be the next card in the order described above.)
At the start of each round, 3 cards are dealt to each player. -Each player plays a card in hand. The player with the highest card will win that hand and discard first in the next hand.
-The first park to get two hands, wins the round. If there is a tie for 3 hands in a row, no one scores points.) First pair to get 12 points wins the game.
It is said "hand of 11" when one of the pairs already has 11 points.

If they do not play the round, the opponents win the round and score 1 point. If they agree to play the round and do not win, the opponents earn 3 points. It is said "iron hand" if both pairs have 11 points. It is normal to throw a card. The winners of this round will be the winners of the game.

UI_Game880_Help_1,"At the beginning of the game,2 cards will be automatically distributed to the dealer and the player","गेम की शुरुआत में, डीलर और खिलाड़ी को 2 कार्ड स्वचालित रूप से वितरित किए जाएंगे",ในตอนเริ่มเกม ไพ่ 2 ใบจะถูกแจกจ่ายให้กับเจ้ามือและผู้เล่นโดยอัตโนมัติ,"At the beginning of the game,2 cards will be automatically distributed to the dealer and the player",遊戲開始時，2張牌會自動分配給莊家和閒家,"Khi bắt đầu trò chơi, 2 lá bài sẽ được chia tự động cho nhà cái và người chơi","Di awal permainan, 2 kartu akan dibagikan secara otomatis ke dealer dan pemain","At the beginning of the game,2 cards will be automatically distributed to the dealer and the player","At the beginning of the game,2 cards will be automatically distributed to the dealer and the player","No início do jogo, 2 cartas serão distribuídas automaticamente para o dealer e o jogador","Al comienzo del juego, se distribuirán automáticamente 2 cartas al crupier y al jugador.",,
UI_Game880_Help_Tip,"The cards are dealt one by one, the player is dealt first and the banker is dealt after. The total points of the 3 cards are 9 points or the one closest to 9 points is the winner, and no cards will be dealt after 3 cards","कार्ड एक-एक करके बांटे जाते हैं, खिलाड़ी पहले और बैंकर बाद में बांटे जाते हैं। 3 पत्तों के कुल अंक 9 अंक हैं या जो 9 अंकों के सबसे करीब है वह विजेता है, और 3 पत्तों के बाद कोई पत्ता नहीं बांटा जाएगा",ไพ่จะถูกแจกทีละใบ ผู้เล่นจะได้รับไพ่ก่อน และเจ้ามือจะได้รับไพ่ทีหลัง แต้มรวมของไพ่ทั้ง 3 ใบคือ 9 แต้ม หรือแต้มที่ใกล้เคียง 9 มากที่สุดเป็นผู้ชนะ และจะไม่มีการแจกไพ่หลังจากไพ่ 3 ใบ,"The cards are dealt one by one, the player is dealt first and the banker is dealt after. The total points of the 3 cards are 9 points or the one closest to 9 points is the winner, and no cards will be dealt after 3 cards",發牌一張一張發，先發閒家後發莊家，3張牌總點數為9點或最接近9點者為勝，3張牌後不再發牌,"Các quân bài được chia lần lượt, người chơi được chia trước và nhà cái được chia sau, tổng điểm của 3 quân bài là 9 điểm hoặc người nào gần 9 điểm nhất là người thắng cuộc, sau 3 quân bài sẽ không được chia quân bài nào.","Kartu dibagikan satu per satu, Player dibagikan terlebih dahulu dan Banker dibagikan setelahnya.Total poin dari 3 kartu adalah 9 poin atau yang terdekat dengan 9 poin adalah pemenangnya, dan tidak ada kartu yang akan dibagikan setelah 3 kartu","The cards are dealt one by one, the player is dealt first and the banker is dealt after. The total points of the 3 cards are 9 points or the one closest to 9 points is the winner, and no cards will be dealt after 3 cards","The cards are dealt one by one, the player is dealt first and the banker is dealt after. The total points of the 3 cards are 9 points or the one closest to 9 points is the winner, and no cards will be dealt after 3 cards","As cartas são distribuídas uma a uma, o jogador é distribuído primeiro e o banqueiro é distribuído depois. O total de pontos das 3 cartas é de 9 pontos ou o mais próximo de 9 pontos é o vencedor, e nenhuma carta será distribuída após 3 cartas","Las cartas se reparten una por una, el jugador se reparte primero y el banquero se reparte después. Los puntos totales de las 3 cartas son 9 puntos o el más cercano a 9 puntos es el ganador, y no se repartirán cartas después de 3 cartas.",,

UI_Game880_Help_2,"After the card is drawn,the two sides will start to compare the points,and the side closer to 9 will win","कार्ड निकाले जाने के बाद, दोनों पक्ष अंकों की तुलना करना शुरू कर देंगे, और 9 के करीब वाली भुजा जीत जाएगी",หลังจากจั่วไพ่แล้ว ทั้งสองฝ่ายจะเริ่มเปรียบเทียบแต้ม และฝ่ายที่ใกล้ 9 จะเป็นผู้ชนะ,After the card is drawn，the two sides will start to compare the points，and the side closer to 9 will win,抽牌後，雙方開始比較點數，接近9的一方獲勝,"Sau khi rút bài, hai bên sẽ bắt đầu so điểm, bên nào gần 9 điểm hơn sẽ thắng",Setelah kartu ditarik，kedua belah pihak akan mulai membandingkan poin，dan pihak yang mendekati angka 9 akan menang,After the card is drawn，the two sides will start to compare the points，and the side closer to 9 will win,After the card is drawn，the two sides will start to compare the points，and the side closer to 9 will win,"Após a retirada da carta, os dois lados começarão a comparar os pontos, e o lado mais próximo de 9 vencerá",After the card is drawn，the two sides will start to compare the points，and the side closer to 9 will win,,
UI_Game880_Help_2_1,"J, Q, K, 10 points are 0, other cards are calculated according to the face of the card","J, Q, K, 10 अंक 0 हैं, अन्य कार्ड कार्ड के चेहरे के अनुसार गणना किए जाते हैं","J, Q, K, 10 pontos são 0, outras cartas são calculadas de acordo com หน้ารายการ","J, Q, K, 10 pontos são 0, outras cartas são calculadas de acordo com a face da carta",J、Q、K，10點為0，其他牌按牌面計算,"J, Q, K, 10 điểm là 0, các quân bài khác tính theo mặt ngửa","J, Q, K, 10 poin adalah 0, kartu lain dihitung sesuai dengan bagian depan kartu","J, Q, K, 10 pontos são 0, outras cartas são calculadas de acordo com a face da carta","J, Q, K, 10 pontos são 0, outras cartas são calculadas de acordo com a face da carta","J, Q, K, 10 pontos são 0, outras cartas são calculadas de acordo com a face da carta","J, Q, K, 10 pontos são 0, outras cartas são calculadas de acordo com a face da carta",,
UI_Game880_Help_2_2,"When the sum of the cards is greater than or equal to 10, only single digits are taken as the final point, and when it is less than 10, the sum is the final point","जब कार्ड का योग 10 से अधिक या उसके बराबर होता है, तो अंतिम बिंदु के रूप में केवल एक अंक लिया जाता है, और जब यह 10 से कम होता है, तो योग अंतिम बिंदु होता है",เมื่อผลรวมของไพ่มากกว่าหรือเท่ากับ 10 ให้นับเฉพาะหลักเดียวเป็นแต้มสุดท้าย และเมื่อแต้มน้อยกว่า 10 ให้แต้มรวมเป็นแต้มสุดท้าย,"When the sum of the cards is greater than or equal to 10, only single digits are taken as the final point, and when it is less than 10, the sum is the final point",當牌面總和大於或等於10時，只取個位數作為最終點數，小於10時，總和為最終點數,"Khi tổng của các thẻ lớn hơn hoặc bằng 10, chỉ có một số được lấy làm điểm cuối cùng và khi nó nhỏ hơn 10, tổng là điểm cuối cùng","Ketika jumlah kartu lebih besar atau sama dengan 10, hanya satu digit yang diambil sebagai poin terakhir, dan ketika kurang dari 10, jumlahnya adalah poin terakhir.","When the sum of the cards is greater than or equal to 10, only single digits are taken as the final point, and when it is less than 10, the sum is the final point","When the sum of the cards is greater than or equal to 10, only single digits are taken as the final point, and when it is less than 10, the sum is the final point","Quando a soma das cartas for maior ou igual a 10, apenas um dígito é considerado o ponto final, e quando for menor que 10, a soma é o ponto final","Cuando la suma de las cartas es mayor o igual a 10, se toma como punto final solo un dígito, y cuando es menor a 10, la suma es el punto final.",,

UI_Game880_Help_banker_4,"lf player draws a 8, then no need to draw card","LF खिलाड़ी 8 ड्रा करता है, तो कार्ड बनाने की आवश्यकता नहीं है",ถ้าผู้เล่นจั่วได้ 8 แล้วไม่ต้องจั่วไพ่,"lf player drawsa 8, then no needto draw card",如果玩家抽到 8，則無需抽牌,Nếu người chơi rút 8 thì không cần rút bài,"Jika pemain menarik 8, maka tidak perlu menarik kartu","lf player drawsa 8, then no needto draw card","lf player drawsa 8, then no needto draw card","Se o jogador tirar um 8, não há necessidade de comprar a carta","Si el jugador roba un 8, entonces no hay necesidad de robar una carta.",,
UI_Game880_Help_banker_5,"lf player draws a 0,1,8, or 9,then no need to drawcard","अगर खिलाड़ी 0,1,8, या 9 ड्रा करता है, तो कार्ड बनाने की कोई जरूरत नहीं है","ถ้าผู้เล่นจั่วได้ 0,1,8 หรือ 9 ก็ไม่จำเป็นต้องจั่วการ์ด","lf player drawsa 0,1,8, or 9,thenno need to drawcard",如果玩家抽到 0、1、8 或 9，則無需抽牌,"Nếu người chơi rút 0,1,8 hoặc 9 thì không cần rút thẻ","Jika pemain menarik 0,1,8, atau 9, maka tidak perlu menarik kartu","lf player drawsa 0,1,8, or 9,thenno need to drawcard","lf player drawsa 0,1,8, or 9,thenno need to drawcard","Se o jogador comprar um 0,1,8 ou 9, não será necessário comprar uma carta.","Si el jugador saca un 0, 1, 8 o 9, no es necesario sacar una carta",,
UI_Game880_Help_banker_6,"lf player draws a 0,1,8, or 9,then no need to drawcard","यदि खिलाड़ी 0,1,2,3,8, या 9 ड्रा करता है, तो कार्ड निकालने की आवश्यकता नहीं है","ถ้าผู้เล่นจั่วได้ 0,1,8 หรือ 9 ก็ไม่จำเป็นต้องจั่วการ์ด","lf player drawsa 0,1,8, or 9,thenno need to drawcard",如果玩家抽到 0、1、2、3、8 或 9，則無需抽牌,"Nếu người chơi rút bài 0,1,2,3,8 hoặc 9 thì không cần rút bài","Jika pemain menarik 0,1,2,3,8, atau 9, maka tidak perlu menarik kartu","lf player drawsa 0,1,8, or 9,thenno need to drawcard","lf player drawsa 0,1,8, or 9,thenno need to drawcard","Se o jogador comprar um 0,1,2,3,8 ou 9, não será necessário comprar uma carta.","Si el jugador saca un 0, 1, 8 o 9, no es necesario sacar una carta",,
UI_Game880_Help_banker_7,"lf player draws a 6 or 7, Draws card","वाम खिलाड़ी एक 6 या 7, कार्ड खींचता है",หากผู้เล่นจั่วได้ 6 หรือ 7 จั่วไพ่,"lf player draws a 6 or 7, Draws card",如果玩家抽到 6 或 7，則抽牌,"Nếu người chơi rút được 6 hoặc 7, Rút bài","Jika pemain menarik kartu 6 atau 7, Draw","lf player draws a 6 or 7, Draws card","lf player draws a 6 or 7, Draws card","Se o jogador tirar um 6 ou 7, saca a carta","Si el jugador saca un 6 o un 7, roba carta",,

UI_Game890_Help_5,"When a player fails to shoot, part of the failed amount will be deposited in the JACKPOT bonus pool.There is a chance to get JACKPOT bonus for each successful shot.","जब कोई खिलाड़ी शूट करने में विफल रहता है, तो असफल राशि का कुछ हिस्सा जैकपॉट बोनस पूल में जमा किया जाएगा। प्रत्येक सफल शॉट के लिए जैकपॉट बोनस प्राप्त करने का मौका है।","เมื่อผู้เล่นล้มเหลวในการยิง ส่วนหนึ่งของจำนวนเงินที่ล้มเหลวจะถูกฝากไว้ในโบนัสแจ็คพอต มีโอกาสที่จะได้รับโบนัสแจ็คพอตสำหรับการยิงที่สำเร็จแต่ละครั้ง","When a player fails to shoot, part of the failed amount will be deposited in the JACKPOT bonus pool.There is a chance to get JACKPOT bonus for each successful shot.","當玩家射擊失敗時，失敗金額的一部分將存入JACKPOT獎金池。每次成功射擊都有機會獲得JACKPOT獎金。","Khi người chơi bắn không thành công, một phần số tiền không thành công sẽ được gửi vào quỹ tiền thưởng JACKPOT. Có cơ hội nhận được tiền thưởng JACKPOT cho mỗi lần bắn thành công.","Ketika seorang pemain gagal menembak, sebagian dari jumlah yang gagal akan disimpan di kumpulan bonus JACKPOT. Ada peluang untuk mendapatkan bonus JACKPOT untuk setiap tembakan yang berhasil.","ఆటగాడు షూట్ చేయడంలో విఫలమైతే, విఫలమైన మొత్తంలో కొంత భాగం జాక్‌పాట్ బోనస్ పూల్‌లో జమ చేయబడుతుంది. ప్రతి విజయవంతమైన షాట్‌కు జాక్‌పాట్ బోనస్ పొందే అవకాశం ఉంది.","जेव्हा एखादा खेळाडू शूट करण्यात अयशस्वी होतो, तेव्हा अयशस्वी झालेल्या रकमेचा काही भाग JACKPOT बोनस पूलमध्ये जमा केला जाईल. प्रत्येक यशस्वी शॉटसाठी JACKPOT बोनस मिळण्याची संधी आहे.","Quando um jogador não consegue atirar, parte do valor falhado será depositado no conjunto de bônus JACKPOT. UI_Game700_rule1,"Select the betting number; if the value matches the winning dice value, then you win the prize.e.g.: Winning dice value 1, 2 & 6, your betting number is 9, and you win the prize.","सट्टेबाजी संख्या का चयन करें; यदि मूल्य जीतने वाले पासा मूल्य से मेल खाता है, तो आप पुरस्कार जीतते हैं। उदाहरण: जीतना पासा मूल्य 1, 2 और 6, आपकी सट्टेबाजी संख्या 9 है, और आप पुरस्कार जीतते हैं।","เลือกหมายเลขที่จะเดิมพัน หากค่านั้นตรงกับแต้มลูกเต๋าที่ชนะ คุณจะชนะรางวัล ตัวอย่าง: ลูกเต๋าที่ชนะคือ 1, 2 และ 6 หากหมายเลขเดิมพันของคุณคือ 9 และคุณจะชนะรางวัล","Select the betting number; if the value matches the winning dice value, then you win the prize.e.g.: Winning dice value 1, 2 & 6, your betting number is 9, and you win the prize.",選擇投注號碼； 如果該值與中獎骰子值相符，則您中獎。例如：中獎骰子值 1、2 和 6，您的投注號碼為 9，您中獎。,"Chọn số đặt cược; nếu giá trị trùng với giá trị của xúc xắc thắng, thì bạn sẽ giành được giải thưởng. Ví dụ: Xúc xắc thắng có giá trị 1, 2 & 6, số cá cược của bạn là 9 và bạn giành được giải thưởng.","Pilih nomor taruhan; jika nilainya sesuai dengan nilai dadu yang menang, maka anda memenangkan hadiahnya. Contoh: Dadu yang menang bernilai 1, 2 & 6, nomor taruhan anda adalah 9, dan anda memenangkan hadiahnya.","Select the betting number; if the value matches the winning dice value, then you win the prize.e.g.: Winning dice value 1, 2 & 6, your betting number is 9, and you win the prize.","Select the betting number; if the value matches the winning dice value, then you win the prize.e.g.: Winning dice value 1, 2 & 6, your betting number is 9, and you win the prize.","Selecione o número de aposta; se o valor corresponder ao valor do dado vencedor, você ganha o prêmio. Por exemplo: Valor do dado vencedor 1, 2 e 6, seu número de aposta é 9 e você ganha o prêmio.","Seleccione el número de apuesta; si el valor coincide con el valor del dado ganador, entonces usted gana el premio. Por ejemplo: el valor del dado ganador es 1, 2 y 6, su número de apuesta es 9 y usted gana el premio."

UI_Game700_rule2,"If the sum of dice value is greater than or equal to 11, the value is defined big; if the value is less than or equal to 10, the value is defined small.","यदि पासा मान का योग 11 से अधिक या उसके बराबर है, तो मान को बड़ा परिभाषित किया गया है; यदि मान 10 से कम या उसके बराबर है, तो मान को छोटा परिभाषित किया जाता है।",หากผลรวมของแต้มลูกเต๋ามากกว่าหรือเท่ากับ 11 แสดงว่าแต้มใหญ่ หากค่าน้อยกว่าหรือเท่ากับ 10 ค่านั้นจะถูกกำหนดให้เป็นแต้มเล็ก,"If the sum of dice value is greater than or equal to 11, the value is defined big; if the value is less than or equal to 10, the value is defined small.",如果骰子點數之和大於或等於11，則該點數大； 如果該值小於或等於 10，則該值被定義為小。,"Nếu tổng giá trị xúc xắc lớn hơn hoặc bằng 11, giá trị được xác định là lớn; nếu giá trị nhỏ hơn hoặc bằng 10, giá trị được xác định là nhỏ.","Jika jumlah nilai dadu lebih besar dari atau sama dengan 11, nilainya ditentukan besar; jika nilainya kurang dari atau sama dengan 10, nilainya didefinisikan kecil.","If the sum of dice value is greater than or equal to 11, the value is defined big; if the value is less than or equal to 10, the value is defined small.","If the sum of dice value is greater than or equal to 11, the value is defined big; if the value is less than or equal to 10, the value is defined small.","Se a soma do valor dos dados for maior ou igual a 11, o valor é definido como grande; se o valor for menor ou igual a 10, o valor é definido como pequeno.","Si la suma del valor de los dados es mayor o igual a 11, el valor se define como grande; si el valor es menor o igual a 10, el valor se define como pequeño."
UI_Game700_ruleTitle3,3、Odd/Even:,3、विषम/सम:,3.คี่และคู่:,3、Odd/Even:,3、單雙：,3、Lẻ/Chẵn:,3、Ganjil/Genap:,3、Odd/Even:,3、Odd/Even:,3、Ímpar/Par:,"3, par/impar:"
UI_Game700_rule3,"Divide 2 into winning dice value, if the remainder is 1, then the sum value is odd; if the remainder is 0, then the sum value is even.","जीतने वाले पासा मूल्य में 2 को विभाजित करें, यदि शेष 1 है, तो योग का मूल्य विषम है; यदि शेषफल 0 है, तो योग का मान सम है।",ใช้ค่าลูกเต๋าที่ชนะหาร 2 ถ้าเศษเป็น 1 งั้นผลรวมเป็นเลขคี่ ถ้าเศษเป็น 0 ผลรวมเป็นเลขคู่,"Divide 2 into winning dice value, if the remainder is 1, then the sum value is odd; if the remainder is 0, then the sum value is even.",將2除以中獎骰子值，若餘數為1，則和值為奇數； 如果餘數為 0，則和值為偶數。,"Chia 2 cho giá trị xúc xắc thắng, nếu dư 1 thì giá trị tổng là số lẻ; nếu phần còn lại là 0, thì giá trị tổng là số chẵn.","Bagilah 2 menjadi nilai dadu yang menang, jika sisanya 1, maka nilai penjumlahannya ganjil; jika sisanya 0, maka nilai penjumlahannya genap.","Divide 2 into winning dice value, if the remainder is 1, then the sum value is odd; if the remainder is 0, then the sum value is even.","Divide 2 into winning dice value, if the remainder is 1, then the sum value is odd; if the remainder is 0, then the sum value is even.","Divida 2 no valor do dado vencedor, se o resto for 1, então o valor da soma é ímpar; se o resto for 0, então o valor da soma é par.","Divida 2 en el valor de los dados ganadores, si el resto es 1, entonces el valor de la suma es impar; si el resto es 0, entonces el valor de la suma es par."

UI_Game1580_Duringanyspin,"● During any spin, the Maya Treasure Feature may be randomly triggered while the reels are spinning.","● किसी भी स्पिन के दौरान, रीलों के घूमने के दौरान माया ट्रेजर फ़ीचर को बेतरतीब ढंग से ट्रिगर किया जा सकता है।",● ในระหว่างการหมุนใดๆ ฟีเจอร์ Maya Treasure อาจถูกกระตุ้นแบบสุ่มในขณะที่วงล้อกำลังหมุน,"● During any spin, the Maya Treasure Feature may be  randomly triggered while the reels are spinning.","● 在任何旋轉過程中，當捲軸旋轉時，Maya 寶藏功能可能會隨機觸發。","● Trong bất kỳ vòng quay nào, Tính năng Kho báu Maya có thể được kích hoạt ngẫu nhiên trong khi các cuộn phim đang quay.","● Selama putaran apa pun, Fitur Harta Karun Maya dapat dipicu secara acak saat gulungan berputar.","● ఏదైనా స్పిన్ సమయంలో, రీల్స్ తిరుగుతున్నప్పుడు మాయ ట్రెజర్ ఫీచర్ యాదృచ్ఛికంగా ట్రిగ్గర్ చేయబడవచ్చు.","● कोणत्याही फिरकीदरम्यान, रील फिरत असताना माया ट्रेझर वैशिष्ट्य यादृच्छिकपणे ट्रिगर केले जाऊ शकते.","● Durante qualquer rodada, a Característica Tesouro Maya pode ser ativada aleatoriamente enquanto os cilindros estao a rodar.","● Durante cualquier giro, la Función del Tesoro Maya puede activarse aleatoriamente mientras los carretes están girando."
UI_Game1580_DuringtheFortune,"● During the Maya Treasure Feature, a symbol is  randomly chosen( exluding Wild symbol) ,  and the symbol will fill the entire reel.","● माया ट्रेजर फ़ीचर के दौरान, एक प्रतीक को यादृच्छिक रूप से चुना जाता है (वाइल्ड प्रतीक को छोड़कर), और प्रतीक पूरी रील को भर देगा।","● ในระหว่างฟีเจอร์ Maya Treasure สัญลักษณ์จะถูกสุ่มเลือก (ไม่รวมสัญลักษณ์ Wild) และสัญลักษณ์จะเต็มทั้งวงล้อ","● During the Maya Treasure Feature, a symbol is  randomly chosen( exluding Wild symbol) ,  and the symbol will fill the entire reel.","● 在瑪雅寶藏功能中，會隨機選擇一個符號（百搭符號除外），該符號將填滿整個捲軸。","● Trong Tính năng Kho báu Maya, một biểu tượng được chọn ngẫu nhiên (không bao gồm biểu tượng Wild) và biểu tượng sẽ lấp đầy toàn bộ guồng.","● Selama Fitur Harta Karun Maya, sebuah simbol dipilih secara acak (tidak termasuk simbol Wild), dan simbol tersebut akan memenuhi seluruh gulungan.","● మాయ ట్రెజర్ ఫీచర్ సమయంలో, ఒక గుర్తు యాదృచ్ఛికంగా ఎంపిక చేయబడుతుంది (వైల్డ్ గుర్తును మినహాయించి) , మరియు గుర్తు మొత్తం రీల్‌ను నింపుతుంది.","● माया ट्रेझर वैशिष्ट्यादरम्यान, एक चिन्ह यादृच्छिकपणे निवडले जाते (जंगली चिन्ह वगळून), आणि चिन्ह संपूर्ण रील भरेल.","● Durante a Característica Tesouro Maya, e escolhido aleatoriamente um símbolo (excluindo o símbolo Wild) e o símbolo preencherá todo o rolo.","● Durante la Función del Tesoro Maya, se elige un símbolo al azar (excluyendo el símbolo Wild) y el símbolo llenará todo el carrete."
UI_Game1580_Afterallreels,● The Maya Treasure feature ends and wins are paid.,● माया ट्रेजर सुविधा समाप्त हो जाती है और जीत का भुगतान किया जाता है।,● ฟีเจอร์ Maya Treasure สิ้นสุดลงและจะได้รับเงินรางวัล,● The Maya Treasure feature ends and wins are paid.,● 瑪雅寶藏功能結束並支付獎金。,● Tính năng Kho báu Maya kết thúc và người chiến thắng sẽ được trả tiền.,● Fitur Maya Treasure berakhir dan kemenangan dibayarkan.,● మాయ ట్రెజర్ ఫీచర్ ముగుస్తుంది మరియు విజయాలు చెల్లించబడతాయి.,● माया ट्रेझर वैशिष्ट्य संपते आणि जिंकले जातात.,● O Característica Tesouro Maya termina e os ganhos são pagos.,● La Función del Tesoro Maya termina y se pagan los premios.

UI_Game1580_Whenallsymbol,"● When all symbol in the reels are involved in a win, the win will be multiplied by x5.","● जब रीलों के सभी प्रतीक जीत में शामिल होते हैं, तो जीत को x5 से गुणा किया जाएगा।",● เมื่อสัญลักษณ์ทั้งหมดในวงล้อมีส่วนร่วมในการชนะ การชนะจะถูกคูณด้วย x5,"● When all symbol in the reels are involved in a win, the win will be multiplied by x5.","● 當捲軸上的所有符號均參與贏獎時，贏獎金額將乘以 x5。","● Khi tất cả biểu tượng trong guồng đều tham gia vào một chiến thắng, số tiền thắng sẽ được nhân x5.","● Ketika semua simbol dalam gulungan terlibat dalam kemenangan, kemenangan akan dikalikan dengan x5.","● రీల్స్‌లోని అన్ని చిహ్నాలు విజయంలో పాల్గొన్నప్పుడు, విజయం x5తో గుణించబడుతుంది.","● जेव्हा रीलमधील सर्व चिन्हे विजयात गुंतलेली असतात, तेव्हा विजयाचा x5 ने गुणाकार केला जाईल.","● Quando todos os símbolos nos cilindros estiverem envolvidos num ganho, o ganho será multiplicado por x5.","● Cuando todos los símbolos de los carretes participan en una premio, éste se multiplica por 5."
UI_Game1580_Standachance,● Stand a chance to win up to 1000x of the total bet amount.,● कुल दांव राशि का 1000 गुना तक जीतने का मौका पाएं।,● มีโอกาสชนะรางวัลสูงถึง 1000x ของจำนวนเงินเดิมพันทั้งหมด,● Stand a chance to win up to 1000x of the total bet amount.,● 有機會贏得高達總投注金額1000倍的獎金。,● Có cơ hội giành được giải thưởng lên tới 1000 lần tổng số tiền đặt cược.,● Dapatkan peluang memenangkan hingga 1000x dari total jumlah taruhan.,● మొత్తం పందెం మొత్తంలో గరిష్టంగా 1000x గెలుపొందే అవకాశాన్ని పొందండి.,● एकूण बेट रकमेच्या 1000x पर्यंत जिंकण्याची संधी मिळवा.,● Tenha hipotese de ganhar até 1000x o montante total da aposta.,● Aprovecha la oportunidad para ganar hasta 1000 veces la cantidad total apostada.
